cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with computer vision and natural language processing, specifically using text to train visual features. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses topic modeling, which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning, which is a common topic in cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with information retrieval, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with multi-modal content, which is a topic in cs.MM (Multimedia).
